---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Lucas Wang">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Hello! I'm Lucas Wang, a software engineer with a passion for building high-quality, 
        performant, and user-friendly web applications.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Background</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I've been working in the tech industry for several years, with experience across the 
        entire stack. From building responsive frontends to architecting complex backend 
        systems, I enjoy the challenge of solving difficult technical problems.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Technical Skills</h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12">
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">TypeScript / JavaScript</li>
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">React / Astro</li>
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">Node.js / Express</li>
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">Go / Distributed Systems</li>
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl font-medium">PostgreSQL / Redis</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Interests</h2>
      <p>
        When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking in the mountains, reading a good book, 
        or experimenting with new recipes in the kitchen. I'm also a big fan of open-source 
        and love contributing back to the community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
